class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="georgian-bay-spirit-co" class="entry-website-title">Georgian Bay Spirit Co.</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-georgian-bay-spirit-co-desktop-3840x10342-20240610.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-georgian-bay-spirit-co-desktop-3840x10342-20240610.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-georgian-bay-spirit-co-desktop-3840x10342-20240610.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Georgian Bay Spirit Co."
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://www.georgianbayspiritco.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://www.georgianbayspiritco.com/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Collingwood, Ontario, Canada</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Georgian Bay Spirit Co. is an award-winning craft distillery that produces a wide range of high-quality alcoholic beverages, including gin, vodka, and whisky. The website's minimalist design elements effectively communicate the company's character, denoting ideas of quality and balance.</p><p>Visitors are introduced to the brand's product offerings with a stylized hero image of their anniversary-addition gin, along with an introductory paragraph that places an emphasis on the distillery's location.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The well-spaced page layouts ensure visitors can easily browse the website, which features an engaging product page with high-resolution images. The use of large typography and ample white space on the home page ensures optimal readability.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>WAVE picked up several errors on the website, indicating insufficient contrast between some of the headings and the blue background. The text on the "Drinks" page is quite small and hard to read, which may impact overall usability.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-georgian-bay-spirit-co-desktop-3840x10342-20240610.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-georgian-bay-spirit-co-desktop-3840x10342-20240610.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop site presents a straightforward user experience, embracing clean lines and sleek aesthetics to allow the high-quality images to shine. The home page's large headings ensure optimal readability, but other pages have smaller text that could be sized up for a better reading experience. On Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the website's SEO and best practices are both optimal with 100/100 scores.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-georgian-bay-spirit-co-mobile-824x10034-20240610.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-georgian-bay-spirit-co-mobile-824x10034-20240610.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The mobile website remains user-friendly and attractive with crisp images, although the hero image is missing. While users can easily find vital information on the site, the hamburger menu and search tool aren't sticky, which may impact the overall user experience. Contrary to real-world experience, the website has an average PageSpeed performance score of 50/100.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
class="entry-container entry-container-content"><div
