alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop website leans on clean and professional design elements rather than content-dense pages to advertise the company's products, creating a simple yet user-friendly experience. The dark background theme allows the lighter text to pop and ensures easy readability, although the social media links in the top-right corner and in the footer menu could be enlarged.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-edinburgh-whisky-824x11281-20240610_2024-06-11-101848_vcnf.webp"
