class="entry-text"><p>The mobile site performs well with seamless navigation and tasteful design elements that allow the high-resolution images and content to shine. The shopping experience remains straightforward and users can easily contact the company via its online form. However, according to Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the website's page loading times are quite slow and PageSpeed performance score is average at 50/100.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
