class="force-single-line" href="https://www.bushrum.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://www.bushrum.co.uk/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>England, U.K.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Bush Rum produces traditional Guyanese rum blended with tropical fruits and spices in the U.K. The website's vibrant color scheme and fun design elements create a cohesive branding experience focusing on Caribbean flair — the dynamic imagery and island-style motifs blend nicely with the informative content and page layouts.</p><p>The company emphasizes its environmentally-conscious approach to rum making with a comprehensive section on its recyclable packaging and sales donations to ocean-focused charities.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>Visitors can peruse the website's selection of content-rich pages and learn more about the company's sustainability practices, its diverse product range, cocktail suggestions, and online purchases. The "In The Press Section" lends credibility to the site with a variety of client testimonials.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The website does not perform well on WAVE's accessibility test, which picked up a large number of contrast errors. A more comprehensive "About" section would add a personable touch to the site, as would images depicting the distillery and/or staff members.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-bush-rum-3840x11534-20240611.webp"
