</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The website allows users to explore the distillery's product range with ease, and the inclusion of detailed product descriptions is ideal for serious buyers. While the company is currently not offering tours, the addition of an online contact form and location map ensures visitors know where to find the distillery for a tasting experience.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>According to WAVE, the website has several contrast errors. While the site does not feature an online shop, pricing can be added to the product descriptions to give users a more holistic overview. The addition of blog posts or a news section would increase the website's overall appeal.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-victoria-distillers-3840x10055-20240611.webp"
